{"type": "article", "id": 18729, "title": "轮伞草系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-09T07:10:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122403oJs3d7tepXQ6gv4c.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t轮伞草是阿美族编织草席的材料，台湾的设计团队 Kamaro’an 用这种材料设计了 4 件家具，包括置物格、名片座、旋草灯和浪草灯。置物格和名片座都是在轮伞草中插入物件，而两种灯则更多使用传统工艺做出有设计感的旋转造型，光线透过轮伞草的缝隙透射下来，很柔和。<a href=\"http://www.zeczec.com/projects/kamaro-an\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122401pLew294s0xOWrm63.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122401eBg4dYKkq1sD8PUm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071224021rFIGxM7mVKetznj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122402QePJ6I0qotv7ByE8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122403ZwdpTju8yoQSCFGr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}